data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Waterford Estates subdivision! This stunning ranch boasts over 3200 sq ft of meticulously designed living space, offering both comfort and style. Step inside to discover a spacious layout featuring vaulted ceilings with skylights throughout the home for a flood natural light. The kitchen features newer stainless-steel appliances. The 2 car garage walks into the main floor mudroom and includes Samsung washer and dryer. Entertain guests effortlessly in the bright and airy living areas, or outside in the spacious private yard that backs to trees, complete with deck and patio. Whether you're hosting intimate gatherings or lively get-togethers, this home provides the ideal backdrop for every occasion. The finished lower level offers even more versatility with two additional sleeping areas both with closets and a large rec room. Roof 2018, HVAC 2022, Appliances 2022.
